    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "My phone buzzed as I wonder if there is something missing."
            ],
            [
                "A single message from Helpie hit me with realization."
            ],
            [
                "Hey… Where are you? the event is going to start soon"
            ],
            [
                "so better hurry if you want to find a good table!"
            ],
            [
                "THE QUICK-DATE EVENT! HOW COULD I FORGET?!?! "
            ],
            [
                "That’s right, after this event I was 100% guaranteed to find a partner."
            ],
            [
                "And to be honest, I wanted to find love more than anything in the world."
            ],
            [
                "Still… I forgot about it. "
            ],
            [
                "Maybe it was a sign... But as my phone kept buzzing with Helpie’s messages"
            ],
            [
                "I realized there was no time to think, it was time to RUN."
            ],
            [
                "Luckily, the cafeteria where the event would take place wasn’t too far away,"
            ],
            [
                "so It would probably take me 3 minutes to get there. "
            ],
            [
                "I approach the cafeteria, and my quick steps start becoming slower and slower, just to suddenly stop."
            ],
            [
                "There was this hopeless feeling that I tried to push away ever since I signed up to this."
            ],
            [
                "but overall, the question: ¿Am I really going to find true love here?"
            ],
            [
                "I thought you wouldn’t make it! Hurry! Let’s go and get you registered."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie began dragging me before I could protest. But maybe it was for the best."
            ],
            [
                "As I enter the cafeteria, I couldn’t help but feel overwhelmed by"
            ],
            [
                "all the corny hearts that conformed the decor of the place."
            ],
            [
                "but I really couldn’t blame the organizers for"
            ],
            [
                "choosing to go with a very on-the-nose theme for a dating event. "
            ],
            [
                "Helpie sat me on an empty table and handed me a presentation card. "
            ],
            [
                "Here"
            ],
            [
                "fill out this nametag so that others can know your name and your preferences!"
            ],
            [
                "Please let me know when you’re done."
            ]
